      "author": "OneCalmCloud",
      "description": "## v1.0.0\r\n\r\n### New Features\r\n\r\n- Dark mode support\r\n\r\n### Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n- Fixed i18n fallback language; non-Chinese locales now default to English\r\n- Fixed issue where Frontmatter properties were being overwritten\r\n- Fixed text color in dark mode — mind map text now correctly displays in light color under dark theme\r\n- Fixed background color in dark mode — defaults to transparent when no background is set, and adapts to dark backgrounds in dark mode\r\n- Fixed compatibility issues with Obsidian multi-pane layout\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n\r\n- Node line colors are now properly saved and will persist correctly on next launch",
